description:
Advantages:
- Functional;
- Fast (uses C++ & Qt);
- Small size (52 MB on Kubuntu 24.04, flatpak);
- Super-advanced (Git vertioning, portable mode, auto-update etc).

Disdvantages:
- Only the NextCloud/ownCloud support. Can be opted-out;
- Only three style themes (Windows, Breeze & Fusion);
- RAM intensive (it eats up to 350 MB RAM with my 136 notes, Kubuntu 24.04).
